ames can be played with 2-4 players, any empty slots can be filled with AI! So you can play solo vs AI if you wish!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/938680/extras/ec35349072eb8f3024f949ef349dff58.avif?t=1631311516\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
